title: Aramanja - Memories (Dawnchaser's Run To The Mountains Bootlegs)
description:
Artist: Aramanja
Title: Memories
Original Release Date: 9-2005
Label: Trancetribe Recordings

Download The Originals On Amazon:

Start Your Adventure With Dawnchaser @:
www.adventuretrance.com
www.reverbnation.com/kulshanrecordings

In 2005, Aramanja released a pair of epic trance tunes named Memories. 
In years since, the label it was released on disappeared, and the tracks 
have almost entirely disappeared from download stores. And now in 2013, it's back. Dawnchaser didn't 
want it to vanish off the face of the Earth, so he set out to do a bootleg mix of his own of 
the tune, and in the spirit of adventure and freedom, he gives it to you now, as a special free
tune.
